0-04T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"係其他ig見到<br />\nSpread them out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509d906a916f27addb2cff0e8d7b8c65e03623aa","tid":1618994,"uid":70859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"對唔住借個位<br />\n18區開花，唔好去政總<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1619215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1619215</a><br />\n<br />\n行政署向政府總部的員工發電郵，指政總員工可以在今日下午3時半後下班。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有政總員工表示，多名警察在午飯時間手持槍枝進入政總戒備。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=3a033269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484230-20191004.htm&h=9b6f7ca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484230-20191004.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n金鐘佢地已經打到熟晒<br />\n知道晒我地有咩不足、點樣可以捉到最多人<br />\n而家已經有晒部署駐晒兵<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔好再打冇把握嘅仗，去返自己地頭，遍地開花！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"02279b57edf0e061c0943a722feb2a0bd019a47d","tid":1618994,"uid":198813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cc8eba86501c0f9361cfa9fb4f807ebf304f6bc7","tid":1618994,"uid":286423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba0d82e417c302535edf196e83e071b6d6fc9349","tid":1618994,"uid":286423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VvxSoUG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvxSoUG.png&h=159043ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/04/153550_2af56e77edaf274c26f62f1689b5bf3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F04%2F153550_2af56e